ActSocial Sciences and Humanities Research Council Act
PrecisRe-appointment of WARREN EDWARD HEWITT of Ottawa, Ontario, as President of the Social Sciences and Humanities Research Council, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective March 1, 2020.
